    <item>
      <title>铜“相当不错”，Artemis Investment Mgmt。说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-24/copper-pretty-well-set-artemis-investment-mgmt-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Artemis Investment Management 全球股票主管表示，他喜欢“铜在供需平衡方面的动态”。亚历克斯·斯坦尼奇在彭博电视上发表讲话时表示，企业方面对铜的兴趣，就像必和必拓试图收购英美资源集团的情况一样，表明铜价“已经相当不错”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-24/copper-pretty-well-set-artemis-investment-mgmt-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 10:03:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
